narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: I learned a lot about Russia in the early 20th century and the early years of the Soviet Union. I feel that my ability to conduct research and convey my ideas in papers has increased during my time in this class.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: I think the course felt disorganized. I never had a clean grasp of what was going on in Russia on a macro level, and the class did not feel as though it built to much.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: I definitely recommend this course! The material is interesting and it was taught very well.
